title: Adobe CS4 for Dummies e-book Collection
description:
This torrent is a collection of the popular "For Dummies" tutorial guides for the Adobe CS4 programs Dreamweaver, Flash, InDesign, and Photoshop.

All e-books are in colour except for the Dreamweaver tutorial guide.

All files are unzipped (is that an old-fashioned word now?).

Enjoy my friends,

If you need something else just ask. Unfortunately I don't have the time to upload all the tutorials I have but if you request it, then I promise I will upload it within a day because you're all lovely people I'm sure. 

:)
